# вҡ–пёҸ AI-Based Case Posting & Lawyer Engagement System

A full-stack web application that connects clients with lawyers using AI-powered case classification and smart matching. This platform simplifies legal assistance by enabling users to post cases, find suitable lawyers, and manage legal interactions efficiently.

