## вҡҷпёҸ Installation & Setup

### 1пёҸвғЈ Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/AI-Based-Case-Posting-and-Lawyer-Engaged-System.git
cd AI-Based-Case-Posting-and-Lawyer-Engaged-System
```

---

### 2пёҸвғЈ Install dependencies

#### Backend

```bash
cd backend
npm install
```

#### Frontend

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
```

---

## рҹ”җ Environment Variables

Create a `.env` file inside the `backend` folder:

```
PORT=5000
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
STRIPE_SECRET=your_stripe_key
```

---

## в–¶пёҸ Run the Project

### Start Backend

```bash
cd backend
npm start
```

### Start Frontend

```bash
cd frontend
npm run dev
```

